COBRA cavity) shows good\nscalability of the preconditioner with up to 3,000 processors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Nov 2017 12:12:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Oct 2018 16:50:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 6 Mar 2019 13:16:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-23"}
